      "title": "3. HOST RESOURCES (Docker Stats - Physical Machine)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Minikube container CPU usage from host perspective (run 'docker stats minikube' on host to see current value)",
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "mappings": [], "max": 100, "min": 0, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "yellow", "value": 50}, {"color": "orange", "value": 75}, {"color": "red", "value": 90}]}, "unit": "percent"}},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 51},
      "id": 14,
      "options": {"orientation": "auto", "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false}, "showThresholdLabels": false, "showThresholdMarkers": true},
      "pluginVersion": "10.2.2",
      "targets": [{"expr": "docker_cpu_percent", "refId": "A", "legendFormat": "Host CPU"}],
      "title": "Host CPU Usage (Docker)",
      "type": "gauge"
    },
    {
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Minikube container memory usage from host perspective (run 'docker stats minikube' on host to see current value)",
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "mappings": [], "max": 100, "min": 0, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "yellow", "value": 50}, {"color": "orange", "value": 75}, {"color": "red", "value": 90}]}, "unit": "percent"}},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 51},
      "id": 15,
      "options": {"orientation": "auto", "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false}, "showThresholdLabels": false, "showThresholdMarkers": true},
      "pluginVersion": "10.2.2",
      "targets": [{"expr": "docker_memory_percent", "refId": "A", "legendFormat": "Host Memory"}],
      "title": "Host Memory Usage (Docker)",
      "type": "gauge"
    },
    {
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Minikube container memory usage in bytes from host perspective",
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}, "custom": {"axisCenteredZero": false, "axisColorMode": "text", "axisLabel": "", "axisPlacement": "auto", "barAlignment": 0, "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "gradientMode": "none", "hideFrom": {"tooltip": false, "viz": false, "legend": false}, "lineInterpolation": "smooth", "lineWidth": 2, "pointSize": 5, "scaleDistribution": {"type": "linear"}, "showPoints": "never", "spanNulls": true, "stacking": {"group": "A", "mode": "none"}, "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "off"}}, "mappings": [], "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]}, "unit": "bytes"}},
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 59},
      "id": 16,
      "options": {"legend": {"calcs": ["mean", "max", "last"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true}, "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "none"}},
      "targets": [{"expr": "docker_memory_bytes", "refId": "A", "legendFormat": "Host Memory Bytes"}],
      "title": "Host Memory Usage (Bytes)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "",
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "custom": {"align": "auto", "cellOptions": {"type": "auto"}}, "mappings": [], "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]}}},
      "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 67},
      "id": 17,
      "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "## Host Metrics Setup\n\nThe **HOST RESOURCES** section shows metrics from the Docker stats perspective (physical machine) vs the cluster-internal metrics.\n\n### Current Status\n\n| Metric | Docker Stats | Cluster Metrics |\n|--------|--------------|----------------|\n| **CPU** | Run `docker stats minikube` on host | Node CPU Utilization % above |\n| **Memory** | Run `docker stats minikube` on host | Node Memory Utilization % above |\n\n### To Enable Host Metrics:\n\n1. **Run on your host machine** (where minikube runs):\n\n```bash\n# Create metrics directory\nmkdir -p /tmp/node_exporter_textfile\n\n# Create collection script\ncat > /tmp/docker-stats.sh <<'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\nSTATS=$(docker stats minikube --no-stream --format \"{{.CPUPerc}},{{.MemUsage}},{{.MemPerc}}\")\nCPU=$(echo \"$STATS\" | cut -d',' -f1 | sed 's/%//')\nMEM_FULL=$(echo \"$STATS\" | cut -d',' -f2)\nMEM_USAGE=$(echo \"$MEM_FULL\" | grep -oP '^\\d[\\d.]*')\nMEM_UNIT=$(echo \"$MEM_FULL\" | grep -oP '\\d[\\d.]*\\s*\\K[MG]iB' | head -1)\nMEM_PERCENT=$(echo \"$STATS\" | cut -d',' -f3 | sed 's/%//')\nif [ \"$MEM_UNIT\" = \"GiB\" ]; then\n  MEM_BYTES=$(echo \"$MEM_USAGE * 1024 * 1024 * 1024\" | bc | cut -d'.' -f1)\nelse\n  MEM_BYTES=$(echo \"$MEM_USAGE * 1024 * 1024\" | bc | cut -d'.' -f1)\nfi\ncat > /tmp/node_exporter_textfile/docker_stats.prom <<PROM\n# HELP docker_cpu_percent CPU from host\n# TYPE docker_cpu_percent gauge\ndocker_cpu_percent{container=\"minikube\"} $CPU\n# HELP docker_memory_bytes Memory from host\n# TYPE docker_memory_bytes gauge\ndocker_memory_bytes{container=\"minikube\"} $MEM_BYTES\n# HELP docker_memory_percent Memory percent from host\n# TYPE docker_memory_percent gauge\ndocker_memory_percent{container=\"minikube\"} $MEM_PERCENT\nPROM\nEOF\nchmod +x /tmp/docker-stats.sh\n\n# Add to cron (runs every minute)\n(crontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep -v docker-stats; echo \"*/1 * * * * /tmp/docker-stats.sh\") | crontab -\n```\n\n2. **The metrics will appear in this section** after:\n   - Node-exporter reads the textfile collector\n   - Prometheus scrapes the metrics\n   - Grafana refreshes the dashboard\n\n### Understanding the Difference\n\n- **Host Metrics (Docker)**: What minikube container uses on your physical machine\n- **Cluster Metrics (Node-exporter)**: What workloads use inside the minikube VM\n- **The difference** is overhead from VM emulation and system services"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "vector(0)", "refId": "A"}],
      "title": "Setup Instructions",
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
